{"tid":1757263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意唔重要","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:39.000Z","uid":288199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6aede183696266d5ba781eb348b20045d639e2","tid":1757263,"uid":288199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"我真係好想問一問成日話唔洗理民意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔洗理民意即係做自己想做既野啦，咁算民主？<br />\n唔理民意憑咩覺得唔會變到當年雨革咁？<br />\n唔洗理民意點解一開始講不割席不篤灰不分化？<br />\n咁民意到底係重要定唔重要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">事後檢討今次區議會個重點只有一個，代表大多數人既意願，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">64比例既票數</span></span>，當佢地有水份，但都有人懶或者受到排隊師影響放棄，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至少都有73</span></span>，佢地有成三成民意係咩原因？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2df6c6364975c69d570ea116703c74f3b194332","tid":1757263,"uid":288199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a8075716c13b9686c116ba834ab06af3150c695c","tid":1757263,"uid":288199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}